{"tid":1997493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗利特已經戒左用IG私CHAT","createTime":"2020-05-01T16:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T18:51:42.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5990df3fe116d8dee2a6ef181b5154eeb9c5dd18","tid":1997493,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"兩週內三度受害 利特 Instagram 再度遭人試圖盜用 <br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e8719e24ff862cae5f0ee8aa0d0fdfde/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-05-01/126382-836399.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e8719e24ff862cae5f0ee8aa0d0fdfde%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-05-01%2F126382-836399.png&h=a344cee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過短短一週左右，利特就兩度透露自己的 SNS 遭他人試圖盜用，身為藝人真的無時無刻不承受莫大的壓力啊！<br />\n<br />\n利特今天（1 日）下午在自己的 Instagram 上發出一張朦朧不清的照片，並簡單明瞭地寫道「不要再駭了，真的。」<br />\n<br />\n日前利特便在自己的 Instagram 上問道：「請問為什麼要盜用心動（寵物狗名）的 Instagram？ㅠㅠ拜託放過心動吧，真的，麻煩您了。」翌日又透露連在凌晨時分都會一直收到（帳號）被盜用的簡訊，表示：「我的壓力真的不是普通大，拜託住手ㅠㅠ。」讓人得知藝人經營 SNS 和粉絲互動，卻得承受這種難以理解的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n即使像利特已經出道多年，依然無法擺脫私生的各種騷擾、對個資的侵犯，真的希望大家都能理性追星和做人啊！"},{"pid":"dbe507b1f19ef7b5a1eb652196b9923ef659b3c4","tid":1997493,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"好sad"},{"pid":"095cc6b6920a17bfe2f24ef4bd7b5d36b1a41fe8","tid":1997493,"uid":3189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/174113_1d7e34ad93d8870cfefcbfb3146c5584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F174113_1d7e34ad93d8870cfefcbfb3146c5584.jpg&h=c726e3f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f4512d6fb9e090307a369299621c9a8c70e203f","tid":1997493,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:48:00.000Z","msg":"老mk都唔知玩過妍雨小胸部幾多次"},{"pid":"e36fe85c68a1c65d7cd9433579f133308429fc6e","tid":1997493,"u